body:
It seems like PushGenericNamespace and PopGenericNamespace always have to be called in pairs (pushing and popping a GenericNamespace to the stack). But the initial GenericNamespace that is pushed (the comment states "as a simplification") doesn't have a corresponding pop.

@karllessard, do you have any comments about this fix
